<i>I must've used salt</i>
<i>instead of sugar!</i>

00:16:00.967 --> 00:16:02.804
Oh my gosh!
Huh?

00:16:02.904 --> 00:16:05.476
Sorry, everyone! You don't
have to eat those!

00:16:05.576 --> 00:16:08.249
I messed 'em up!
I cannot believe this!

00:16:08.349 --> 00:16:10.286
I'm really sorry!

00:16:11.087 --> 00:16:12.457
It's okay...

00:16:12.557 --> 00:16:14.561
They're perfectly fine.

00:16:14.661 --> 00:16:16.665
I really do like them
a lot.

00:16:16.765 --> 00:16:19.136
Give them to me
and I'll eat the rest.

00:16:20.273 --> 00:16:21.642
Huh?

00:16:21.742 --> 00:16:24.146
(Twinkling)
Wha...?

00:16:29.156 --> 00:16:33.566
I like really sweet things, and
I like really salty things, too.

00:16:33.666 --> 00:16:34.968
I mean it.

00:16:35.068 --> 00:16:37.674
Is there any food out
there you DON'T like?

00:16:37.774 --> 00:16:39.878
Hm? Not really.

00:16:41.180 --> 00:16:42.817
(Giggle)

00:16:44.086 --> 00:16:45.223
(Sigh)

00:16:45.323 --> 00:16:48.295
Okay, Takeo, what is it YOU
like about Rinko Yamato?

00:16:48.395 --> 00:16:50.700
AH! Oh god! Where is
all this coming from?!

00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:52.069
