around on him or what.

00:17:37.994 --> 00:17:42.135
But... she has a secret.
I know it.

00:17:42.704 --> 00:17:44.139
[TAKEO]
Oh, wow...

00:17:44.240 --> 00:17:45.476
Huh?

00:17:45.576 --> 00:17:46.979
[TAKEO]
Take a look at the sky.

00:17:47.079 --> 00:17:49.784
The stars are really
beautiful again tonight.

00:17:51.254 --> 00:17:53.392
[RINKO]
Yes. They are.

00:17:54.995 --> 00:17:57.400
They're smiling on us.

00:18:08.288 --> 00:18:09.457
[RINKO]
Takeo...

00:18:09.557 --> 00:18:10.993
Hm?

00:18:11.093 --> 00:18:14.434
You know, I... Uh...

00:18:14.801 --> 00:18:16.170
Huh?

00:18:16.271 --> 00:18:19.043
